唔難，不時有啲金銀珠寶賞賜，又有啲神兵利器。同埋一兩個人自己用錢都有限。<br />\n<br />\n最難明係啲乜派物派，丐幫可以乞食，少林可以化緣，咁華山崆峒果啲呢？一個門派百幾人，日日都練功，都唔知邊度有錢開飯"},{"pid":"d1a041672f1ece97eff8e32545a6ee6a4e2f6e39","tid":320700,"uid":14977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"周伯通放係而家會唔會係男人之光？溝左條二世祖既大波妹，中出完大埋肚即飛"},{"pid":"8ca089e7999c44c8b54500fed427f25bf19ccc40","tid":320700,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"金庸小說不嬲無經濟系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上外國小說點都會有講經濟，例如D劍客去幫財主打工，或者主角無錢靠屋企人接濟。<br />\n<br />\n但金庸大俠個個都揮金如土，從來唔駛揾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fed5ce220d35419da461da695188cc039364990","tid":320700,"uid":482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相反點解蕭峰係丐幫幫主但咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十一奉獻都要問？"},{"pid":"5445a310c6538298474f8a0c5258f9b5d871b938","tid":320700,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>相反點解蕭峰係丐幫幫主但咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十一奉獻都要問？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真<br />\n蕭峰仲係幫主嗰時洗費入哂分舵數一蚊都唔使自己出<br />\n唔係幫主嗰時係入官府定銀行偷錢買酒飲"},{"pid":"28a8db0624b8af0674c1a5105adb367f736491b8","tid":320700,"uid":67329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"全部都係金庸業喎"},{"pid":"02c591fad26b760baee3e9b77f53bfeb65c0c11b","tid":320700,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"樓主返工返到shot q咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd3b11fcc3be8e1ddb542cb900ea5fa8ac4cad2","tid":320700,"uid":86270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"個個都好有諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma